A3-3116, HHA-203 

Medicare covers HHA services when the following criteria are met: 
 1. The person to whom the services are provided is an eligible Medicare beneficiary; 

2. The HHA that is providing the services to the beneficiary has in effect a valid 
agreement to participate in the Medicare program; 

3. The beneficiary qualifies for coverage of home health services as described in 
§30; 

4. The services for which payment is claimed are covered as described in §§40 and 
50; 

